item.title: [HIVE-21294] Vectorization: 1-reducer Shuffle can skip the object hash functions
item.description: VectorReduceSinkObjectHashOperator can skip the object hashing entirely if the reducer count = 1.
item.summary: Vectorization: 1-reducer Shuffle can skip the object hash functions

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.

comments.comment: teddy.choi: you're right, that's the right operator name - it currently computes a hashcode and then does % 1 for 1 downstream reducers.
